ntation is located in dom/serviceworkers/ServiceWorkerEvents.h and dom/serviceworkers/ServiceWorkerEvents.cpp, as FetchEvent is a Service Worker specific event that extends ExtendableEvent. The FetchEvent class is implemented in ServiceWorkerEvents.h/cpp rather than in dom/fetch/ because it represents events dispatched in service worker contexts.\"\n}\n",
